{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Reduce ministerial salaries by 20% in solidarity with furloughed workers",
        "additional_details": "Not all companies made up the 20% shortfall. \r\n\r\nIn solidarity with these workers, I propose that government ministers also take a 20% pay cut. ",
        "background": "The New Zealand Government have taken a 20% pay cut in solidarity with people who have been affected by COVID-19. The UK government has introduced a furlough scheme in which the government will pay 80% of an employees wages up to \u00a32500pm. Its up to the individual companies if they pay the other 20%",
